            <h2>How often should maintenance be scheduled?</h2>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li><strong>Homes:</strong> Annual inspections at minimum. Older homes or large households need more frequent service.</li>
              <li><strong>Businesses:</strong> Every 3 to 6 months, especially restaurants and high-water-use facilities.</li>
              <li><strong>Maintenance plans:</strong> Ongoing expert care throughout the year with regular inspections and scheduled cleanings.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
